    • getAddressName

      protected String getAddressName(String name, String houseNumber)
      Navitia always formats the address label in the French way. This method can be used to display addresses in a localized way. It defaults to putting the house number behind the street name.
      Parameter:
      name - The name of the address. Usually a street name.
      houseNumber - The house number of the address.
      Gibt zurück:
      the localized name of the address location
